{"id":1751,"date":"2024-09-14T19:16:53","date_gmt":"2024-09-14T19:16:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1751"},"modified":"2024-09-14T19:23:21","modified_gmt":"2024-09-14T19:23:21","slug":"heracronite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/heracronite\/","title":{"rendered":"Heracronite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Heracronite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found outside the Black Ferrothorn building in Antisis City after completing the \u201cThe Battle of Antisis\u201d mission.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Heracross<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Antisis City<\/li>\n<li>Complete <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-061\/\">\u201cThe Black Emboar\u201d<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Complete all other missions Black Emboar missions in the city<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center and go east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/heracronite\/01-pokemon-unbound-going-east-from-the-anstisis-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Going east from the Anstisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going east from the Anstisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the last building (just past the mart).<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/heracronite\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-black-emboar-building.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Black Emboar building. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Black Emboar building.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Inside, approach the person north of the table with the side mission bubble on top of his head.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/heracronite\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-npc-who-gives-the-battle-of-antisis.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the NPC who gives \u201cThe Battle of Antisis\u201d \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the NPC who gives \u201cThe Battle of Antisis\u201d<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speaking with him after clearing all the other missions in the building will start the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-060\/\">\u201cThe Battle of Antisis\u201d<\/a> side mission.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/heracronite\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-information-for-the-the-battle-of-antisis-side-mission.jpg\" alt=\"The information for the \u201cThe Battle of Antisis\u201d side mission. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The information for the \u201cThe Battle of Antisis\u201d side mission.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Complete the side mission and speak with the NPC blocking the Black Ferrothorn building to get the Heracronite.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/heracronite\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-npc-who-gives-the-heracronite.jpg\" alt=\"The NPC who gives the Heracronite. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The NPC who gives the Heracronite.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1752,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1751","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1751","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1752"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1751"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1751"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}